{"tid":1361222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港官員除左去大灣區，仲識做乜？","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:38:31.000Z","uid":198829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce368abcd61c3e945a42a1738c18b897a3785cb3","tid":1361222,"uid":198829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"冇其他野識做架啦，繼續當市民ge訴求係唱歌。<br />\n發生元朗恐襲之後，政府唔會諗點解決問題，繼續唔理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己香港，自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聶德權明赴廣西<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月24日<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權明天訪問廣西兩天，與廣西壯族自治區政府代表會面，並參觀大學、企業。<br />\n <br />\n聶德權會考察廣西的最新規劃、陸海新通道的物流和海運發展、廣西與香港在產品質量檢驗方面的合作進展，他也會參觀當地中醫藥大學、職業技術學院和創新科技企業。<br />\n <br />\n聶德權周五傍晚回港，他離港期間，副局長陳帥夫署任局長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/07/20190724/20190724_171910_409.html?type=category&amp;name=admin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F07%2F20190724%2F20190724_171910_409.html%3Ftype%3Dcategory%26name%3Dadmin&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0FuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=36bb3f25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/07/20190724/20190724_171910_409.html?type=category&amp;name=admin</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊明訪廣州<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月24日<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊明日上午前往廣州，到訪廣東省高級人民法院和廣東省司法廳，探討加強雙方合作，晚上返港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/07/20190724/20190724_161137_782.html?type=category&amp;name=admin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F07%2F20190724%2F20190724_161137_782.html%3Ftype%3Dcategory%26name%3Dadmin&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0FuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=d91d24b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/07/20190724/20190724_161137_782.html?type=category&amp;name=admin</a>"},{"pid":"9bb4857b6b6e850aab0e4e02e94bea35b39dca3b","tid":1361222,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"去call g <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afabffa00f08d8acbf4b548c734b86d9539416cd","tid":1361222,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}